definitions.definition: A location or restaurant where good food can be expected, or an instance of eating at such a place.
examples: Sally is having a breakfast munch at her place!
We had a good munch at the chippy.

definitions.definition: A casual meeting for those interested in BDSM, usually at a restaurant , bar or pub .
Someone who easily agrees to give oral sex .
